# Configuration plane — activated (real) config objects. Templates (*.example)
# ARE committed; a customer's real org/autonomy/model policy must NEVER land in
# the reference repo. Activate by copying the .example, then point the
# orchestrator at it via ORG_MODEL_PATH / AUTONOMY_PATH (see config/README.md).
config/org.yaml
config/autonomy.yaml
config/models.yaml
/org.yaml
/autonomy.yaml
/models.yaml
